{"tid":1671893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全球抗暴】大熱兒歌《Baby Shark》 意外成為黎巴嫩示威歌曲","createTime":"2019-10-23T19:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T23:19:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58eab0846a420c8ea62f267d7aeea3abf12c8d3b","tid":1671893,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T19:02:52.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫩爆發反政府示威，民眾抗議政府加稅及貪腐等問題。在示威浪潮當中，大熱兒歌《Baby Shark》卻意外成為了示威者在集會時高唱的歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n杰伯（Eliane Jabbour）上周駕車經過首都貝魯特（Beirut）示威區時，她問示威者可否不要吵醒她的15個月大兒子羅賓（Robin）。此時車外約20人圍着杰伯的車輛，一邊高興地向她們唱着兒歌《Baby Shark》，一邊拍手模仿鯊魚合口的動作，其中一名留有鬍子的男人在人群中扮魚游泳。<br />\n<br />\n杰伯拍下這一幕並上載到網上，片段之後獲廣泛流傳，成為了當地的示威歌曲。Twitter周日有片段顯示，示威者揮舞黎巴嫩國旗一邊唱着《Baby Shark》。雖然羅賓在片段中顯得不為所動，但杰伯指兒子已愛上了這首歌，「儘管他在片段中看起來很困惑，但現在他每次見到它就會笑」。<br />\n黎巴嫩政府上周四宣佈新的稅收政策，包括向使用WhatsApp等通訊應用程式徵收每月6美元（47港元）的通話稅項，令民眾對政府貪腐、管理不善和裙帶關係的憤怒一瞬間爆發。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191023/large/1571811897_cd7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191023%2Flarge%2F1571811897_cd7a.jpg&h=97f714d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n群眾圍着車輛唱兒歌《Baby Shark》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191023/60184961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F60184961&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=7bca6f8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F60184961&h=dbc757bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191023/60184961</a>"},{"pid":"ed694ffb21e9cc997654715c12d9a9c0cb785b51","tid":1671893,"uid":96664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"成班似嚇親細路多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c633e8f040efd1055c23dafbfb7663bd25a03d2","tid":1671893,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed694ffb21e9cc997654715c12d9a9c0cb785b51","tid":1671893,"uid":96664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"成班似嚇親細路多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:08:35.000Z","msg":"外表問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530e2adcae0a04410b37eff7e117962f7bf43096","tid":1671893,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1dc9b7e1fcb506f24e07196e95c2b6d5e3ae35","tid":1671893,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}